    {"parentUuid":"bb61a426-f314-4eaf-9dbb-d8dbe2fce0f7","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"b51d0d0e-11a7-49cc-a304-5ddf3d02ce8f","agentId":"a9a175726ae9963f1","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TCpha2HN9WH4ifDxm496RR","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"arxiv 2101.08773 \"Summing mu(n)\" faster elementary algorithm Helfgott Thompson O(x^{3/5})\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"[2101.08773] Summing $μ(n)$: a faster elementary algorithm\",\"url\":\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2101.08773\"},{\"title\":\"(PDF) Summing $\\\\mu(n)$: a faster elementary algorithm\",\"url\":\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/348675384_Summing_mun_a_faster_elementary_algorithm\"},{\"title\":\"Summing $$\\\\mu (n)$$ : a faster elementary algorithm | Research in Number Theory | Springer Nature Link\",\"url\":\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s40993-022-00408-8\"},{\"title\":\"SUMMING µ(n): A FASTER ELEMENTARY ALGORITHM\",\"url\":\"https://people.maths.bris.ac.uk/~jb12407/ANTS-XV/papers/ANTS-XV_helfgott-thompson.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"(PDF) Summing $$\\\\mu (n)$$: a faster elementary algorithm\",\"url\":\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/366126419_Summing_mu_n_a_faster_elementary_algorithm\"},{\"title\":\"[PDF] Summing μ ( n ) : a faster elementary algorithm. | Semantic Scholar\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Summing-%CE%BC-(-n-)-:-a-faster-elementary-algorithm.-Helfgott-Thompson/53e96664644bdb6481f429761791df75ddf00df1\"},{\"title\":\"Summing μ(n): a faster elementary algorithm\",\"url\":\"https://pure.mpg.de/pubman/item/item_3486843_2/component/file_3486847/Helfgott-Thompson_Summing+mu(n)_a+faster+elementary+algorith_2023.pdf\"},{\"title\":\"Summing μ(n): a faster elementary algorithm - PMC - NIH\",\"url\":\"https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC9731940/\"},{\"title\":\"Summing [... formula ...]: a faster elementary algorithm - PMC\",\"url\":\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC9731940/\"},{\"title\":\"arXiv:2101.08773v4 [math.NT] 28 Feb 2022\",\"url\":\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2101.08773\"}]\n\nI found the paper! Here are the search results for arxiv 2101.08773:\n\n## Paper Summary\n\nThe paper presents a new elementary algorithm for computing M(x) = ∑_{n ≤ x} μ(n) (the sum of the Möbius function) that takes time O_ε(x^{3/5} (log x)^{3/5+ε}) and space O(x^{3/10} (log x)^{13/10}).\n\n## Key Contributions\n\nThis is the first improvement in the exponent of x for an elementary algorithm since 1985.\n\nSpace consumption can be reduced to O(x^{1/5} (log x)^{5/3}) by using earlier work (Helfgott, 2020), at the cost of letting time rise to the order of x^{3/5} (log x).\n\n## Authors\n\nThe paper is authored by Harald A. Helfgott and Lola Thompson.\n\nThe paper was originally posted on arxiv on January 21, 2021, and was later published in the journal *Research in Number Theory*.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"0ad6d3ff-cd1e-47a9-a04f-79f5a427b9b7","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:12:35.387Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"bb61a426-f314-4eaf-9dbb-d8dbe2fce0f7","userType":"external","entrypoint":"sdk-cli","cwd":"/apps/aplikacijos/prime-research","sessionId":"33140f23-a580-4bd9-95f3-32a2246a99e4","version":"2.1.92","gitBranch":"main","slug":"majestic-juggling-whale"}
